Currently I work in the developers Team at Actualis. I love talking about Data Science, Data Wrangling, analyzing and visualizing. I am also interested about Forecasting, Data Modeling, Tennis, Basketball and Foods üçù (particularly Empanadas, Pastries & Desserts).
